{{Top|rwm}}
'''Making Episode III Webdocs''' was a feature on the ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace]] fan club website. It showcased eighteen web-based documentaries covering the production of [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']]. The movies were available in two [[:Wikipedia:QuickTime|QuickTime]] sizes: 480 x 270 for Hyperspace subscribers and 320 x 180 for non-members. The webdocs were later included on the Episode III second DVD.

